    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is a total gem\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, you won't find a single scratch or hiccup anywhere. It\u2019s been my absolute baby, but it's finally time for it to find a new home. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new and drives like a dream, this is definitely the one for you! Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
