      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe, finished in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained with a focus on mechanical longevity: the rod bearing service is complete, the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced with structural plates. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the telepathic handling these chassis are known for. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and original paint depth across all panels, this is a turn-key example for the collector seeking peak naturally aspirated performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
