    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard that rivals its original showroom debut. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of imperfections, chips, or swirls. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery shows no wear and still carries its original scent, while every electronic component and switch functions with factory-fresh precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive folder of preventative maintenance records from authorized specialists. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. For the discerning buyer seeking a flawless, investment-grade example, this is an unparalleled opportunity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
