      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car, so it's in truly pristine, spotless condition inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
